instance.description: Hippocampal-prefrontal recordings in rats (dorsal CA1 region of the hippocampus and primarily the prelimbic region of prefrontal cortex) during exposure to novel and familiar WTrack environments. Data includes spikes from single units, local field potential recordings, position (x, y, velocity), and trajectory information. Each file contains data from 3 behavioral epochs - Novel Wtrack (first exposure) - Familiar WTrack - Novel WTrack (second exposure)
